  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/4595e05e296c64261cf1531453d4ebb8.poster.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/4595e05e296c64261cf1531453d4ebb8.webm?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/4595e05e296c64261cf1531453d4ebb8.mp4?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Manage your own architecture firm! Would you prefer to design one skyscraper or many residences, or maybe all at once? Create buildings, beautify the city, sell land plots, manage a warehouse, hire employees, buy real estate, and watch your health.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/9da1a14a3fa83cbafc63290f95a7b652.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=96 /></span><br>Turn any idea into reality! Create everything from a small garage to a huge skyscraper. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/945faaea6e2636c0b2bc9ae64dc8a933.poster.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/945faaea6e2636c0b2bc9ae64dc8a933.webm?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/945faaea6e2636c0b2bc9ae64dc8a933.mp4?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/2b31de2ce90f89dea928726768309298.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=96 /></span><br>Buy resources when prices drop and spot the best deals.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/d026200cd20819aa4a5f455399fe3694.poster.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/d026200cd20819aa4a5f455399fe3694.webm?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/d026200cd20819aa4a5f455399fe3694.mp4?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/0669ed0820e75fe16450ef2ebba999ab.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=96 /></span><br>It is impossible to handle such a complex business alone. Hire a staff that will make your job much easier.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/eff2f6f9ad2ca865337bcbc8c7453687.poster.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/eff2f6f9ad2ca865337bcbc8c7453687.webm?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/eff2f6f9ad2ca865337bcbc8c7453687.mp4?t=1735236019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2977070/extras/39307302ae2a00b2245d7db0ed6b6d4d.avif?t=1735236019\" width=618